OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain, and fairly
OL,7,Fwidespread haar. It will become dry
OL,8,Flater in the night, with the haar
OL,9,Fclearing Orkney towards the morning.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FShetland damp with some
OL,12,Fhaar in the morning then brightening
OL,13,Fup in the afternoon with sunny
OL,14,Fintervals. Orkney dry for much of day,
OL,15,Fsome sunny intervals, then showers
OL,16,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
