OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FThursday and early Friday mostly
OL,7,Fcloudy with some showery rain, then
OL,8,Flater Friday and Saturday mainly dry
OL,9,Fand bright with some sunshine.
